      "span_text": "This finding is similar to a recent finding by Cai and colleagues that Blacks undergoing knee/hip arthroplasty were more likely than Whites to be admitted to hospitals with higher risk-adjusted postoperative rates of complications or mortality [CITATION_1] ."
